{"tid":2351361,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好同兔兔沖涼呀...","createTime":"2021-01-03T06:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T07:36:55.000Z","uid":197098,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d38aefa4f132adcd97c0212c5d66627643966e4b","tid":2351361,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:55:19.000Z","msg":"兔子很愛乾淨，會自動自己清理洗澡。同兔仔洗澡是很危險，會令牠精神創傷，嚇怕到呆和僵硬，經常這樣會心臟病發。但有一個例外: 如果牠們屁股被糞便粘住(poopy butthole), 可以給屁股洗澡🛁(butt bath), 但不要用手直接拉糞便出來，因為會連皮拉出來。要用水浸到肛門和腳然後慢慢清理，不用任何沐浴乳或肥皂:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6UcoZHBlQ80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6UcoZHBlQ80&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0PSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=20159c27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6UcoZHBlQ80</a><br />\n<br />\n如果主人試過同兔子洗澡，可能見過兔子用後腳站起來，左右手上下方向擦。這時候兔子其實不是同你玩水，這個姿態是代表不高興，想主人不要理會牠。以下video可看到主人給兔子洗澡時，兔子在3:26被嚇暈:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6zkyjfOq36g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6zkyjfOq36g&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0PSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=2d47f57c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6zkyjfOq36g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">資訊來源:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://rabbit.org/the-dangers-of-giving-a-rabbit-a-bath\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org%2Fthe-dangers-of-giving-a-rabbit-a-bath&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0PSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=e1ae33de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rabbit.org/the-dangers-of-giving-a-rabbit-a-bath</a></span>"},{"pid":"5bbb2441facefe74b5f65626789e4f44e92ac6ee","tid":2351361,"uid":56751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T04:23:23.000Z","msg":"又loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a099b1a9925223c8b1e97d909d9d0926918c93","tid":2351361,"uid":67565,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T04:26:32.000Z","ms